</div>
<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>（尚层实景案例一）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">轻奢，不仅是风格的概括</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">更是一种生活态度的传达</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在现代生活中坚持对生活品质的追求</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那一抹蓝的融入</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">令人感受到皇家蓝的尊贵</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">诠释什么是“轻度的奢侈”</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20200226/e7582c53823b41f9bdf9ff81922473ae.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">灵动的蓝色精灵，在灰与白的交织中滑过</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">没有成群结队地占据多大的空间</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">可一下子就成为了视线的焦点</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20200226/824b165a98214af098e95b7a851ef92a.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">层层叠叠、错落有致</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">吸引人的目光不由自主地去找寻</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">令空间淡雅而不乏味</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">简净而不朴素</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20200226/fc13b41aad1848d894844bdd416477e4.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>蓝调*现代=？</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>（尚层实景案例二）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20200226/1c2ec662e5454db680d48775277cae64.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">把蓝调投入时尚鲜活的现代风</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">欢快的线条能够突破蓝色沉闷的格调</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">尤其是深沉的蓝调在空间中大面积铺开的时候</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">整个空间流淌着醉酒般的惬意</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20200226/652a397041d24277a899f0b90f8dfb2b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">回归家里</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在吧台边微醺</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">卸下一切武装与烦累</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在如同海洋般深邃的蓝色中</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">恣肆徜徉</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20200226/d5e683e58be9442990d24932668c51fd.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">橙色，甚至是对比色的黄色，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">都被蓝调宽容地接纳，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">同时，也帮助蓝色从阴郁的性格中脱离，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">从此，品茗不再单调，聚友也不再浮躁。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20200226/e1f591ab8ba54aafbd59c8e9a0c460bc.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>蓝调*混搭=？</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>尚层实景案例三</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20200226/081e2d13615041498359fcf0c2f9de9e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不同饱和度的蓝调色块，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">藏匿着一分清透、一分空灵，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">少许的一点寂寞也被植株的自然生机冲淡。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20200226/6417d75a6f46470ba16bc21e7a804aae.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">钟情于美式的自在，用蓝色和壁炉的熨帖</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">赋予家温暖且稳重的气息</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">再与角落里的金框挂画</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">来一场浪漫雅致的邂逅</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20200226/1fee718917e648b2be8d9e1ad4bf72f0.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">蓝调，想起星空与海洋的浩瀚深邃</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">皇家蓝的高贵典雅，梵高《星月夜》的神秘</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">汲取自蓝色的情怀</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">悠游在平和浪漫中无以自拔蓝调，在设计师专业的把控力下，融入轻奢、现代，以及更多的意境中，令家流露出不一的情绪。</p>